channel.title: [508] OMG 508 run error [508]
channel.description:
I recently came back to RSPS and have been coding a new 508, however i have been coding the source no problems and managed to get it up and running.. But today i added 100% Godwars Dungeon and now i get this error when i run my server.. How do i fix it?
